title: IAA Tonight | Why Draymond Avoided Suspension
description: Leger Douzable and Antoine Walker discuss the report on the reason why Draymond Green wasn't suspended by the Golden State Warriors. The guys also discuss Ben Simmons responding to a viral video and a chat on Commanders DB Will Jackson III seemingly wanting out of Washington, DC.
author: smanderville@houseofathlete.com (Leger Douzable, Antoine Walker)
